window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Escape to the Gulf Coast of Florida with Georgia Carpenter as she gets a second chance at life, love, and happiness.</p> <p>With a hurricane barreling toward Blackbird Beach, Georgia Carpenter is faced with new problems and the need to work faster than ever. The last thing she needs is more damage to the inn, but she can’t control nature.</p> <p>What she can control is how the people around her weather that storm. In a bid to protect those she loves, she pulls them all close, opening her new home as a place of shelter.</p> <p>Everything’s going fine, too, until the man she’s falling for, Travis Taylor, reveals he has a storm of his own going on. Will the changes in his life mean changes in Georgia’s too?</p>"; 
